title: COMPANY Node Type
data_structure:
\[
  {
    "name": "name",
    "mandatory": true,
    "datatype": "string",
    "example": "BMW AG"
  },
  {
    "name": "founded",
    "mandatory": false,
    "datatype": "number",
    "example": "1916"
  },
  {
    "name": "defunct",
    "mandatory": false,
    "datatype": "number",
    "example": ""
  },
  {
    "name": "headquarters\_location",
    "mandatory": false,
    "datatype": "string",
    "example": "Munich"
  },
  {
    "name": "legal\_headquarters\_location",
    "mandatory": false,
    "datatype": "string",
    "example": "Munich"
  }
]
